      "content": "but that's the thing, it feels kinda pointless to even want to have an impact if it's all just going to be gone anyway. it's like being on a plane that's clearly going down—why bother trying to fix a seat or something? i just feel like i'm stuck in this loop of being terrified of a future that's already decided. it's just so exhausting to keep existing in a world that's clearly reaching its end.",
